b2f97","tid":335911,"uid":30006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T04:32:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家啲新既自動泊車 係咪S L位都掂？ 香港咁窄有冇難度？</blockquote><br />\n泊位果d我反為唔大concern，主動安全關到自己條命緊要d"},{"pid":"9c4b87671f4af83fc38272393b0278c639478b80","tid":335911,"uid":30006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T04:33:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>睇到上面兩個留言，我就覺得同香港講科技真係無撚用。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一日講支付科技，就同我講番有八達通就夠。</blockquote><br />\n你老母生你出來就無撚用，唔係話自動駕駛無用，係話你個point廢呀<br />\n有錢邊個唔想出架新車，仲有新車都唔係架架有SAE個standard，你就叫人唔好出二手車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁你得幾皮野　我無野講，<br />\n好多時你手頭d 錢，可以買十年前二手超靚車，或者買新平車with科技，又或者買無科技但又型的新車<br />\n<br />\n我只係想講如果你夠錢，考慮一架有科技主動安全足的車，比你買個牌子或買個樣有建設性</blockquote><br />\n但係事實有好多人買部車唔係為左d科技安全<br />\n係為左買番d以前嘅經典<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n明的，有錢出部NSX任性下，點會諗呢d科技野"},{"pid":"a37ec1b741060b06a7452826b780b2229fd9f1a3","tid":335911,"uid":17345,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T04:38:24.000Z","msg":"買完新車，年年兩三年又換車？以你概念，一有新科技就要換車啦喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 商用車巴士果啲點算？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7340035b97e27c77af8855fc7ddba307fafbbfb0","tid":335911,"uid":3937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T04:38:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港多車路窄又成日整路 會唔會update唔切?</blockquote><br />\n雷達/lidar 係睇即時路況<br />\n<br />\n個人覺得就係咁（多車路窄又成日整）先更加有用"},{"pid":"d204310def40c941a9f36e02ff196bced2f2193b","tid":335911,"uid":18241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T04:38:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>戇鳩揸咗咁多年咪又係咁揸 係咪無科技你就唔撚識揸車</blockquote><br />\n不如騎返馬la"},{"pid":"e2c44e58f4363477bc213bf1cce136c5df111b12","tid":335911,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T04:48:34.000Z","msg":"而家係聰明到，隔離車係你盲點扭軚撞你，部電腦會自動幫你扭軚避開 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n隔離有車點算?"},{"pid":"db07bf286bd33ca88f5a2da43f301edc5c384e12","tid":335911,"uid":46231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T04:48:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>睇到上面兩個留言，我就覺得同香港講科技真係無撚用。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一日講支付科技，就同我講番有八達通就夠。</blockquote><br />\n你老母生你出來就無撚用，唔係話自動駕駛無用，係話你個point廢呀<br />\n有錢邊個唔想出架新車，仲有新車都唔係架架有SAE個standard，你就叫人唔好出二手車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁你得幾皮野　我無野講，<br />\n好多時你手頭d 錢，可以買十年前二手超靚車，或者買新平車with科技，又或者買無科技但又型的新車<br />\n<br />\n我只係想講如果你夠錢，考慮一架有科技主動安全足的車，比你買個牌子或買個樣有建設性</blockquote><br />\n但係事實有好多人買部車唔係為左d科技安全<br />\n係為左買番d以前嘅經典<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n明的，有錢出部NSX任性下，點會諗呢d科技野</blockquote><br />\n所以唔反對樓主你話科技安全嘅重要 不過都唔可以否定以前d車嘅價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔同嘅人都有唔同嘅需要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c04af063b583992da4822c9a70a8b25658723d54","tid":335911,"uid":46231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T04:49:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家係聰明到，隔離車係你盲點扭軚撞你，部電腦會自動幫你扭軚避開 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n隔離有車點算?</blockquote><br />\n又扭番另一邊 最後兩邊都不停有車 最後就蛇行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c80008bfaecadee8328da489c637ee23a52b6f2","tid":335911,"uid":100474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T04:51:49.000Z","msg":"唔太完全同意你講嘅野<br />\n當然呢啲新嘅功能就係為左安全<br />\n但你話人會攰會分心呢啲我就唔同意<br />\n因為作為司機你要專心守規則（兩秒距離）呢啲係應份<br />\n講到好似理應會分心咁，然後話一定要有呢啲功能去幫你<br />\n如果個司機精神狀態不足以揸車，就算有呢啲功能都唔應該揸車，呢啲野係附助性質<br />\nTesla之前美國單野就係因為simulate足夠嘅路面情況<br />\n同埋好似之前香港條片，個司機剎車同車速冇拎好平衡一樣會失控<br />\n當然有好過冇，新好過舊<br />\n但最後都係睇司機，唔一定要有"},{"pid":"9843b6ed34e88f9fd0ae23339d30ccf433d4dbac","tid":335911,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T04:58:04.000Z","msg":"用錢買科技 但買唔到技術"},{"pid":"49cc84c1108565cf30c7b8bfb8fbeb857188a106","tid":335911,"uid":21028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T04:58:47.000Z","msg":"之前有單model x 太子道西炒上巴士站撞傷兩條友 點計？"},{"pid":"be946a2ea951a3129f5342495c70d287644bf0c3","tid":335911,"uid":130225,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T05:06:58.000Z","msg":"電子野、雷達、sensors唔會攰, 你冇錯, 但會壞會出錯...<br />\n其實渣車渣到電腦幫埋你睇路轉彎, 不如搭車啦識落車就搞掂。<br />\n<br />\nP.S. 90年車車主"},{"pid":"e0b7ac58f7892b9ae517a620b6cdd17d66f4185f","tid":335911,"uid":21222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T05:14:19.000Z","msg":"諗起強國條片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 測到有人自動停點知撞到條友仆街"},{"pid":"60f2f3134fcc659478da2bd65dbc929544e44207","tid":335911,"uid":21222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T05:16:43.000Z","msg":"除非法律話你呢部車既科技幫到你唔會撞到人，撞到就係車商既責任咁我就買"},{"pid":"5e4b2113d34cffb9ecc9c19ffc77ac20c9661f70","tid":335911,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T05:18:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>除非法律話你呢部車既科技幫到你唔會撞到人，撞到就係車商既責任咁我就買</blockquote><br />\n發覺樓主真係好天真<br />\n好多實際問題都唔理"},{"pid":"e8361eec8db66f98a3b79107f00fce425933173c","tid":335911,"uid":3527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T05:22:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>電子野、雷達、sensors唔會攰, 你冇錯, 但會壞會出錯...<br />\n其實渣車渣到電腦幫埋你睇路轉彎, 不如搭車啦識落車就搞掂。<br />\n<br />\nP.S. 90年車車主</blockquote><br />\n其實係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n全世界所有車都自動駕駛就唔會有安全問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但如果server 俾人hack嘅話<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"057eef78147843bdd9a2cb518ee84e2027c6bcf8","tid":335911,"uid":54066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T05:23:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>而家係聰明到，隔離車係你盲點扭軚撞你，部電腦會自動幫你扭軚避開 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n隔離有車點算?</blockquote><br />\n又扭番另一邊 最後兩邊都不停有車 最後就蛇行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個功能係city 真係無用 ， 隨時避右線車撞左邊車 、保險要自己賠 、右線車就話之你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5845c2411b6a7a533d6a5fd755a7b4fedc0bbbb0","tid":335911,"uid":28007,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T05:34:43.000Z","msg":"成日都話安全安全 揸車係種樂趣黎架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n乜撚野都唔使做咁我不如去搭車好過<br />\n同埋本身揸車司機就有責任去提起十二分精神留意路面情況<br />\n依家啲人連車都揸唔好就要靠電腦<br />\n老實講我寧願信自己都好過信部濕鳩電腦"},{"pid":"000359389fcb60e8bbf3c2a8e2b3768aa99848cc","tid":335911,"uid":33004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T05:44:00.000Z","msg":"打一大篇垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n撘巴士啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80941907484be844d13fa55f300cad1fb7859b93","tid":335911,"uid":57962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T05:53:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5755e68015a3ec426019e8d70748814f34c590b9","tid":335911,"uid":21432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T05:56:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇到上面兩個留言，我就覺得同香港講科技真係無撚用。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一日講支付科技，就同我講番有八達通就夠。</blockquote><br />\n屌 你解決左的法律問題先黎講科技啦<br />\n電腦錯撚左係車廠賠定車主賠呀？<br />\n<br />\n的防滑呀 氣袋呀 剎車防鎖死就真係有用多多聲啦"},{"pid":"78090d6477cae86a1a2651478b6cb2b1ca347ecc","tid":335911,"uid":23763,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T05:56:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>諗起強國條片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 測到有人自動停點知撞到條友仆街</blockquote><br />\n咪就係Volvo囉😂😂😂"},{"pid":"7fc3ba56c990ffcbac34b2d04309d1c2081da1b4","tid":335911,"uid":21432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T05:57:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實樓主講出黎都係想其他車主可以注意多d安全意識<br />\n都唔明點解咁都畀人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢係撚叫人注意，一副眾人皆醉我獨醒咁既死人樣"},{"pid":"983233f00cb45e22813a84ff9c21663ca2e69329","tid":335911,"uid":59030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T06:05:19.000Z","msg":"咁新車又唔可以好似梯r mx5果d咁好操控<br />\n又無舊掃把evo果d咁好玩  渣黎做乜<br />\n大把玩經典車既人就係想部車乜野電子安全系統都唔要先買呢d車"},{"pid":"1d3a5e1e5140806fd6938bb36957cc8427c3f107","tid":335911,"uid":3912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T06:06:55.000Z","msg":"依家呢個年代嘅電腦其實未完善 都係會出錯<br />\n揸車咁危險嘅嘢我認為都係自己人手操作好過信個電腦<br />\n同埋樓上都有巴打講過 買㗎車嚟要享受佢auto功能嘅話，咁不如搭的士，個個買車都係享受自己揸嘅樂趣㗎啦"},{"pid":"40e97cf84297e7b5b62cbc1eb240ed070bd0e62b","tid":335911,"uid":10639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T06:30:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成日都話安全安全 揸車係種樂趣黎架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n乜撚野都唔使做咁我不如去搭車好過<br />\n同埋本身揸車司機就有責任去提起十二分精神留意路面情況<br />\n依家啲人連車都揸唔好就要靠電腦<br />\n老實講我寧願信自己都好過信部濕鳩電腦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為十個香港人至少有一半揸車唔專心<br />\n一日見幾多人一路揸車一路撳電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n根本司機專注係路面已經減少好多不必要嘅意外"},{"pid":"268f8f12750f82870ac0ec186cb9c67747f395d7","tid":335911,"uid":56188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":